[01:31.00]Illusions of the sunlight.
[01:38.00]A reflection of a lie will keep me waiting.
[01:43.00]With love gone for so long.
[01:48.00]
[01:51.00]And this day's ending is the proof of time killing all the faith I know.
[02:04.00]Knowing that faith is all that I hold.

[04:36.00]Yesterday I died, tomorrow's bleeding.
[04:42.00]Fall into your sunlight.
